COMMANDS INDEX

Syntax: commands

Lists every player command, grouped by category. The staff / wizard
section is listed for everyone but only usable by staff.

  ================= PLAYER COMMANDS =================

  skills & abilities    Spells, psionics, skills, abilities
  combat & movement      Combat, movement, and survival
  communication & social Says, channels, radio, mail, social
  systems                Score, advancement, game systems
  commands                Other player commands
  staff / wizard          Staff and wizard commands

  =====================================================

Type help <command> for details on any command in the list.

SEE ALSO: getting-started, syntax, help
